Features
--------
Make 'git su' print only the current derived user when stdout isn't a tty
Make 'git su --local' print more obvious output when stdout _is_ a tty
Make colors configurable because people like that stuff
Make default scope configurable for shared machines
Support multiple users at once for pairing

Bugs
-------
When I type 'git su -c', I see
    fatal: unable to read config file '/etc/gitconfig': No such file or directory
